item.title:
Prince Harry and Meghan Markle were involved in a ‘near catastrophic car chase’ after being chased by paparazzi for two hours in New York.
The paparazzi swarm included cars, motorcycles and scooters and nearly resulted in collisions involving other drivers and pedestrians.
item.author: PopBase

item.title:
Food Network had ordered two new series hosted by Selena Gomez.
The first one will be a ‘celebration-focused series’ debuting in the holiday season, while the second one will have her meeting up with some of the best chefs in the country.
